data.description: Assumable Mortgage Rate 3.49%. Fantastic newly remodeled Farmhouse on over 5 acres! This home features 5 Bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms as 900 square feet of this home was just done Winter 2022 and finished Spring 2023. The NEW Primary Suite features a separate Shower and Soaking Tub, double vanities, as well as 2 barn doors - a beautiful design! The REMODEL also includes All new Countertops in the Kitchen and bathrooms, as well as matte black finished plumbing hardware. Also in 2023 new flooring was added throughout the main level living spaces to complete this MOVE IN READY Home!! The Large Rocking Chair Front porch with 2 Newly Installed ceiling fans make this Country home the PERFECT Place to call home in BELOVED MORGAN COUNTY. This home is in the SOCIAL CIRCLE City, of Morgan County. Don't forget your Basketball Goal and BATTING Cages and Swing Set/Playground for any size family to stay busy on this 5 acre PECAN Tree Farm.
